    "name": "Throw Your Phone (Into The Ocean)",
    "steam_appid": 2138740,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No weapons, no leveling up, no loot, no drama. Escapism for the modern age. Throw Your Phone (Into The Ocean) is a simple game where you can live out your secret fantasy of throwing a series of phones into a series of beautiful bodies of water. A meditative experience and cathartic way to deal with our attachment to technology. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138740/extras/1b29fedc322da950bbf723c5f0f52863.avif?t=1751031994\" width=311 height=200 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138740/extras/93c24bc6b9b49f1006669b7bbf6e34ac.avif?t=1751031994\" width=256 height=262 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Arcade </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Arcade Mode has a simple scoring system and allows you to get competitive with friends. Toss your phones into a series of objectives as they float down the river, drift by your sea-scape or play some strange carnival games. Featuring a local leaderboard, so you can challenge your friends or get competitive with yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138740/extras/93c24bc6b9b49f1006669b7bbf6e34ac.avif?t=1751031994\" width=256 height=262 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138740/extras/55af1d24035506fdd40671634cd57c8d.avif?t=1751031994\" width=355 height=200 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Zen</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zen Mode is the ultimate escape. With no objectives or time limit, take a walk through the palm trees on a moonlit tropical shoreline or witness the northern lights among the pines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138740/extras/c55fba1c3f1db950929c8edb23739007.avif?t=1751031994\" width=700 height=138 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Experience...</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the thrill of your rebellious acts in a series of beautiful environments. With none of the environmental hazards of throwing your real phone into real nature! <i>Throw Your Phone</i> is the responsible choice, and the ultimate simple satire simulator.<br><br>Featuring realistic water as the centerpiece around a series of stylized tranquil environments, this game is a digital vacation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138740/extras/ddebc92216dcf57d5c6e108822b5fd02.avif?t=1751031994\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138740/extras_big/ddebc92216dcf57d5c6e108822b5fd02.avif?t=1751031994 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
